<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-52-0349 </DOCNO><TEXT>The draft of the new text of the CPSU Program provides for further majorprogress in industrial automation in the coming decades involving thechangeover to automatic factor shops and plants as well as automatedcontrol and design systems. Research directed towards what is known asartificial intelligence is closely linked with the accomplishment ofthis goal. Academician GERMOGEN POSPELOV, Chairman of the ArtificialIntelligence Research Council of the USSR Academy of Sciences, told correspondentYuri Samoilov, about progress so far and the outlook for the future.</TEXT></DOC>